panels.description: This panel shows the CPU usage for the Docker containers monitored by Telegraf.

targets.query: SELECT mean("usage_guest") FROM "cpu" WHERE ("host" = 'docker-telegraf' AND "customer" = 'OpenWebinars' AND "os" = 'Linux' AND "environment" = 'Dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
